{
    "_comment": [
        "FHIR R4 Bundle of type 'document' representing the equivalent of a MADO DICOM KOS object.",
        "",
        "KOS IOD → Bundle mapping:",
        "  SOP Common Module        → Bundle.identifier (KOS SOP Instance UID)",
        "  SOP Common Content Date/Time → Composition.date (= KOS Content Date + Time)",
        "  Patient Module           → Patient entry",
        "  General Study Module     → ImagingStudy (study-level fields)",
        "  General Equipment Module → Device entry (MadoCreator)",
        "  Key Object Document Module (Referenced Request Sequence)",
        "                           → ServiceRequest entry (Accession Number + Placer Order)",
        "  SR Document Content (TID 2010 root + TID 1600 Image Library)",
        "                           → Composition.section + ImagingStudy.series",
        "  TID 1601/1602 per series → ImagingStudy.series[] including series descriptors",
        "  TID 1601 per instance    → ImagingStudy.series[].instance[]",
        "  Current Requested Procedure Evidence Sequence (Retrieve URL / Location UID)",
        "                           → Endpoint entries (WADO + XC-WADO)",
        "",
        "NOTE: MadoFhirBundle profile fixes Bundle.type to 'collection'.",
        "This example uses type 'document' as requested, which requires a Composition",
        "as the first entry. The Composition mirrors the KOS SR Document header",
        "(Document Title, Observation DateTime, referenced instances summary).",
        "All resources are contained in full (no external references)."
    ],
    "resourceType": "Bundle",
    "id": "mado-kos-document-bundle-example",
    "meta": {
        "profile": [
            "https://profiles.ihe.net/RAD/MADO/StructureDefinition/MadoFhirBundle"
        ]
    },
